ormance, cost, know-how, business plans, business methods, and process information, disclosed to the Recipient.  For convenience, the Disclosing Party may, but is not required to, mark written Confidential Information with the legend \"Confidential\" or an equivalent designation.2.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1116, "end_char_idx": 1592, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "52949e73-caa3-4f00-9ebb-f80bafcefb60": {"__data__": {"id_": "52949e73-caa3-4f00-9ebb-f80bafcefb60", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "0350dc68-f4c5-498b-854c-c5ebd59507e9", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "286f073f0040a90581da36d5755736b557a183e9d490e0008f7633c9f92bf5b5", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "f5e75db8-f260-404b-86c9-5b5eb81e3259", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "3e1155d626db9d1e28f8ba8a1c5d2c2e4f188e1e658e6c7797b569e343d6c905", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "a10b4ac7-1d8c-4a45-9c80-238d64b1101d", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "ce88877484f4af795ec28be376045c58a54de512518ed057180e4f49cd696d42", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "All Confidential Information disclosed to the Recipient will be used solely for the Business Purpose and for no other purpose whatsoever. The Recipient agrees to keep the Disclosing Party\u2019s Confidential Information confidential and to protect the confidentiality of such Confidential Information with the same degree of care with which it protects the confidentiality of its own confidential information, but in no event with less than a reasonable degree of care.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1595, "end_char_idx": 2059, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}"